response.overview: Alex, Sara, Marcos, Riley, and Laura have been roommates for a long time. When the landlord tells Alex that someone has been illegally subletting the apartment without the others' knowledge, he must do everything he can to find out who is responsible. In the process, some unwanted confessions come to light.
response.tagline: You think you know 'em... do you actually?
response.title: El subarriendo
